    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/a5b27d593efba1ada9d52bfc4546fdef.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个令人惊叹且放松的游戏！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<i>Work Adventure</i>中，你拥有完全的自由做任何事情！无论你是在观看视频或播客、工作，甚至是学习，都可以将游戏开在后台并享受乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大量的战斗！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与生物战斗并收集独家物品！在抢先体验阶段，将会有7组生物，每组至少包含两种生物，每种生物有3到6种变化！这么多可爱的怪物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >养育生物是父母的责任！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于心地柔软的人来说，也可以使用游戏中的道具驯服这些生物！装满你的背包并捕捉所有的小生物，好吗？但请记住，它们的捕捉有特定的时间和道具要求！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我是谁？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是Davi，社交媒体上更广为人知的名字是DevBandeira（YouTube、Udemy等），一名开发者/游戏设计师，同时也是本项目的网页开发者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我决定开发<i>Work Adventure</i>，灵感来源于此类游戏，旨在融入怪物与生物收集游戏的元素，以及与小怪物的直接战斗、属性与资源、收藏品等更多内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/16fafb32903e85a4d6cd16918bbccba6.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=180 /></span></p>",
